summary:
OBLIVIONIZING SKYRIM.

This mod adds quite a lot of stuff, from player homes to dungeons. All lore friendly and challenging.
descriptionHtml:
[b][i]OBLIVIONIZING SKYRIM.

[/i][/b]Did you ever feel like there was something missing?
Do you feel like the world of Skyrim was empty?
Well then this is the [b]mod [/b]for you!

This mod adds a town, 'Sentinel's Watch.'
Adds a few dungeons, such as an Ayleid Ruin near the Jerall Mountains.
The good old Wayshrines (Talos included), with their appropiate map markers.
And much more!
author: Dwemer Archiver
